      "text": "番組をご覧のみなさん、こんばんは\n月のテンペストの成宮すずですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ladies and gentlemen watching the show‚ good evening.\nThis is Suzu Narumiya from Moon Tempest!",
