      "text": "今から、私が敬愛してやまない長瀬麻奈様の曲を\n歌わせていただきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ I will sing a song by my beloved Mana Nagase-sama.\nI will sing it with all my might‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2333333333,
      "endTime": 67.2205781719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
