      "text": "天国にいらっしゃる麻奈様にまで届くように\n大きく、強く、そして素敵に歌い上げてみせますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so that it reaches Mana-sama in heaven.\nI will sing it loudly‚ passionately‚ and beautifully!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7,
      "endTime": 77.174405352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
